{"tid":2342152,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"［有圖，唔恐怖］屋企好多小強，跪求處理方法","createTime":"2020-12-27T02:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T03:52:33.000Z","uid":237900,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"153e5a99ea42d4fca74a9b2345bdd7a07a2494a2","tid":2342152,"uid":237900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T02:08:47.000Z","msg":"屋企最近裝修完<br />\n裝修完後有用過滅蟲煙霧先住番<br />\n但依家每日都見到幾隻呢種微型小強<br />\n研究過好有可能係brown banded cockroach既幼蟲<br />\n有無巴絲可以確認下？<br />\n暫時一隻成年既小強都無見過<br />\n會唔會係滅蟲煙霧殺唔到殘留既蟲卵？<br />\n小強出現最多既地方係我間房<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廚房同其他地方都無咁多<br />\nBrown banded成年會識飛，遲d我一定驚到瀨屎<br />\n有無巴絲有經驗處理過呢種小強？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wDJnKi0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwDJnKi0.png&h=11142404&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thQUAqL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FthQUAqL.png&h=c9b58204&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"045e8e1c41313133dc1dfec093f8e94f11edfe4a","tid":2342152,"uid":112901,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T02:21:01.000Z","msg":"隻甲由死得好得戚"},{"pid":"dfcdbeaf6c5df3f5e4f54bbdcba5b68296d95efd","tid":2342152,"uid":78770,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T02:22:02.000Z","msg":"一點絕<br />\n買一枝返黎點哂全屋 一星期見效"},{"pid":"d5014dfb3ad384fb07a0f1ce584b19c4107d8b04","tid":2342152,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T02:32:53.000Z","msg":"lm<br />\n曾經用好多曱甴藥加埋戰贏住廚房嘅佢地<br />\n依家走左去房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日係床邊發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即刻落返一點絕<br />\n<br />\n買左新藥盒未到"},{"pid":"3774417ce1c81e5d14e7e3a19d1c39dfa7323562","tid":2342152,"uid":44569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T02:34:49.000Z","msg":"黎多次煙彈"},{